		(property "Description" "5V-to-3.3V regulator implemented as a linear converter using AMS1117-3.3. Input capacitor 10uF on VIN, output capacitor 22uF on 3V3_OUT, both referenced to GND. EN may be tied to VIN for always-on operation."
			(at 0 0 0)
